}\n\n                        })                };            </script>        </div>\n```\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\n\n| Candidate | Recognitions | % of Step 5 total |\n|-----------|-------------:|------------------:|\n| DBSCAN cluster | 47\\,554 | 93\\.6 % |\n| Known Product UOM (WAP) | 1\\,300 | 2\\.6 % |\n| EA/1 WAP candidate | 1\\,128 | 2\\.2 % |\n| File UOM × WAP | 816 | 1\\.6 % |\n\n: {.striped .hover}\n\nDBSCAN is the dominant winner (93\\.6 %), validating that\nthe density-based clusters are the most reliable signal.  The remaining 6\\.4 %\nare split across the three supplementary pools — each of which catches a class of products\nthe primary DBSCAN clusters do not yet cover.\n\n---\n\n## Top 10 Assigned UOMs (Step 5)\n\n::: {#425b9013 .cell execution_count=4}\n\n::: {.cell-output .cell-output-display}\n```{=html}\n<div>            <script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/mathjax/2.7.5/MathJax.js?config=TeX-AMS-MML_SVG\"></script><script>if (window.MathJax && window.MathJax.Hub && window.MathJax.Hub.Config) {window.MathJax.Hub.Config({SVG: {font: \"STIX-Web\"}});}</script>                <script>window.PlotlyConfig = {MathJaxConfig: 'local'};</script>\n        <script charset=\"utf-8\" src=\"https://cdn.plot.ly/plotly-3.5.0.min.js\" integrity=\"sha256-fHbNLP+GlIXN+efbQec78UkemUz3NJp7UmfGxC1tNxs=\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>                <div id=\"c10ccd53-0354-4484-abd7-8b71b7bd189c\" class=\"plotly-graph-div\" style=\"height:420px; width:100%;\"></div>            <script>                window.PLOTLYENV=window.PLOTLYENV || {};                                if (document.getElementById(\"c10ccd53-0354-4484-abd7-8b71b7bd189c\")) {                    Plotly.newPlot(                        \"c10ccd53-0354-4484-abd7-8b71b7bd189c\",                        [{\"marker\":{\"color\":\"#27ae60\"},\"orientation\":\"h\",\"text\":[\"22,026\",\"1,819\",\"1,308\",\"1,267\",\"1,254\",\"990\",\"964\",\"949\",\"930\",\"908\"],\"textposition\":\"outside\",\"x\":[2